Package: ros-noetic-mrpt-localization
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ros-noetic-dynamic-reconfigure, ros-noetic-mrpt-libgui, ros-noetic-mrpt-libros-bridge, ros-noetic-mrpt-libslam, ros-noetic-mrpt-msgs, ros-noetic-mrpt-msgs-bridge, ros-noetic-nav-msgs, ros-noetic-pose-cov-ops, ros-noetic-roscpp, ros-noetic-sensor-msgs, ros-noetic-std-msgs, ros-noetic-tf2, ros-noetic-tf2-geometry-msgs, ros-noetic-tf2-ros
Description: Package for robot 2D self-localization using dynamic or static (MRPT or ROS) maps.
 The interface is similar to amcl (https://wiki.ros.org/amcl) but supports different particle-filter algorithms, several grid maps at different heights, range-only localization, etc.
